title: Tazehabad (37°13′ N 49°30′ E), Pasikhan
text: Tazehabad (, also <a href="Romanize">Romanize</a>d as Tāzehābād) is a village in <a href="Pasikhan%20Rural%20District">Pasikhan Rural District</a>, in the <a href="Central%20District%20%28Rasht%20County%29">Central District</a> of <a href="Rasht%20County">Rasht County</a>, <a href="Gilan%20Province">Gilan Province</a>, <a href="Iran">Iran</a>. At the 2006 census, its population was 128, in 32 families.
